summary: The fact Rize doesn’t work for almost anyone who has Android phone makes me so unbelievably and irrationally ANGRY. Like I just...
body:
The fact Rize doesn’t work for almost anyone who has Android phone makes me so unbelievably and irrationally ANGRY. Like I just want to throw my phone away, forget I’ve ever heard of Dan and Phil and find new hobbies. I feel like that one friend not invited to a party.

Yes I know they needed a sponsor for the tour, but they have always before been strict that their content is available for everyone everywhere. So I really really really hope they could at least stream liveshows somewhere accessible (like tumblr or youtube).

The fact Rize doesn’t work for anyone anyway, I’m secretly happy.
